    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people want to help but it doesn't change the math. the numbers don't lie. i'm just looking at these bills and i realize i'm never going to be able to pay them. i'm never going to be able to go back to how things were. it's just a endless cycle of failing. it feels like the only way to actually stop it is to just... stop everything.",
