      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like a trap. no matter what \"step\" i take, the debt just grows. it's like running on a treadmill that's speeding up and i'm about to fall off. if there's no way to actually fix the math, then why keep trying to run? it feels like we're just talking about delaying the inevitable.",
